          <div class="card-main">
            <div><div class="card-zh">纯原则者</div><div class="card-en" style="color:#444">Pure Principled</div></div>
            <div class="card-person"><div class="person-avatar" style="background:#d4ccec">🏺</div><div class="person-name">第欧根尼<span>Diogenes of Sinope</span></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="traits-row">
            <span class="trait-tag" style="background:#ddd6f5;color:#4a34a0">内在标准是唯一的现实</span>
            <span class="trait-tag" style="background:#ddd6f5;color:#4a34a0">零妥协</span>
            <span class="trait-tag" style="background:#ddd6f5;color:#4a34a0">原则高于一切，包括帝王的好意</span>
